overview:
Flying Penguin Offers Kids Toys Sydney Residents Love!

Flying Penguin Extraordinary Educational Toys offers high quality, educational toys and games for children from 0-15 years, carefully chosen to last and produced with minimal negative impact on the environment. Our belief is that young people are the future and investing in products which enrich and sustain young minds will help build an inclusive and positive world.
